has-relation.sql: select distinct doc.fullName from XWikiDocument as doc, BaseObject as ring, StringProperty as hasRelation, StringProperty as hasRelatum where ring.name = doc.fullName and ring.className = 'Ring.Code.RingClass' and hasRelation.id.id = ring.id and hasRelation.id.name = 'has-relation' and hasRelation.value = 'Ring.IsA' and hasRelatum.id.id = ring.id and hasRelatum.id.name = 'has-relatum' and hasRelatum.value = 'Ring.Relation' order by doc.fullName
